        <title type="html"><![CDATA[@hapi/call v2.0.0]]></title>
        <id>https://github.com/hapijs/call/milestone/1</id>
        <link href="https://hapi.dev/module/call/changelog#2.0.0"/>
        <updated>2014-11-23T08:41:31.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[@hapi/call v2.0.0]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li><a href="https://github.com/hapijs/call/issues/10">[#10]</a> Support route id</li><li><a href="https://github.com/hapijs/call/issues/9">[#9]</a> /a/{p}/{p*} conflicts with /a/{p*} (which is not reachable)</li><li><a href="https://github.com/hapijs/call/issues/8">[#8]</a> '/a/b/{p*}' is more specific than '/{p*5}'</li><li><a href="https://github.com/hapijs/call/issues/7">[#7]</a> /a/b/{p*} is more specific than /a/{b}/{c}</li><li><a href="https://github.com/hapijs/call/issues/6">[#6]</a> '/a/{b*}' is less specific than '/a/{b}/{c*}'</li><li><a href="https://github.com/hapijs/call/issues/3">[#3]</a> Support for flexible routes</li><li><a href="https://github.com/hapijs/call/pull/2">[#2]</a> Match case-insensitive paths with no params</li></ul>]]></content>
